This is a sample use of <a href="https://kenenna.com" target="_blank">Kenenna N. Okeke's</a> PHP Single Action Simulation Engine.<br/>It uses a configuration file to draw up I/Os. The UI sends off inputs to the back-end for outputs.<br/>The source code is available on GitHub: <a href="https://github.com/KenennaOkeke/CaffeineJunkieCalculator" target="_blank">https://github.com/KenennaOkeke/CaffeineJunkieCalculator</a>